<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 06:18:18 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国问题削减了宝马第二季度汽车利润率</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/bmws-auto-profit-margin-falls-short-forecast-q2-2024-08-01/</link><description>宝马周四报告称，由于竞争加剧和中国需求疲软影响了这家豪华汽车制造商的销售，第二季度其核心汽车部门的利润率低于预期。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 05:43:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/bmws-auto-profit-margin-falls-short-forecast-q2-2024-08-01/</guid></item><item><title>大众汽车警告称，第二季度利润下降，成本削减阶段尚未结束</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagens-profit-falls-restructuring-costs-weigh-first-half-2024-08-01/</link><description>大众汽车周四警告称，其成本削减期尚未结束，并将持续到 2024 年下半年之后，因为成本上升导致第二季度营业利润下降。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 05:37:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagens-profit-falls-restructuring-costs-weigh-first-half-2024-08-01/</guid></item><item><title>大型卡车制造商押注于氢气以延长内燃机寿命</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/big-truckmakers-bet-hydrogen-extend-combustion-engine-life-2024-08-01/</link><description>包括沃尔沃和曼在内的一些世界上最大的卡车制造商正在改造内燃机，以使用低排放氢气而不是污染柴油，这是解决能源转型挑战的更快、低成本的解决方案，可能会给垂死的技术带来新的生命。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 05:07:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/big-truckmakers-bet-hydrogen-extend-combustion-engine-life-2024-08-01/</guid></item><item><title>日本游客的挥霍行为给奢侈品牌带来了新的头痛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/japan/tourist-splurge-japan-creates-new-headache-luxury-brands-2024-08-01/</link><description>由于日元疲软，游客纷纷涌入日本以折扣价购买高端服装和手袋。路易威登母公司路威酩轩集团等奢侈品公司宁愿他们呆在家里购物。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 05:01:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/japan/tourist-splurge-japan-creates-new-headache-luxury-brands-2024-08-01/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：市场押注仁慈的英国央行</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-08-01/</link><description>Stella Qiu 展望欧洲和全球市场未来一天</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 04:34:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-08-01/</guid></item><item><title>中国工厂低迷给亚洲制造商带来压力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-economy-chinas-factory-gloom-weighs-asias-manufacturers-2024-08-01/</link><description>周四的私人调查显示，由于企业主努力应对需求不温不火的情况，中国制造业活动的低迷导致上个月亚洲工厂的表现普遍疲弱，这增加了该地区经济复苏动力不足的风险。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 04:28:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-economy-chinas-factory-gloom-weighs-asias-manufacturers-2024-08-01/</guid></item><item><title>东京世锦赛男子和女子 100 米决赛定于第二天举行</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/athletics/mens-womens-100m-finals-scheduled-day-two-tokyo-world-championships-2024-08-01/</link><description>世界田径理事会（WAC）周三表示，男子和女子 100 米决赛将于明年在东京举行的世界田径锦标赛第二天举行。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 02:41:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/athletics/mens-womens-100m-finals-scheduled-day-two-tokyo-world-championships-2024-08-01/</guid></item><item><title>全球科技股飙升、日元上涨，亚洲股市上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-08-01/</link><description>亚洲股市周四上涨，跟随 Meta 和 Nvidia 帮助下的科技股大幅复苏，而美国即将放松政策的前景提振了全球债券和大宗商品。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 02:06:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-08-01/</guid></item><item><title>PMI调查增加前景风险，中国工厂准备迎接“残酷的夏天”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-factory-activity-contracts-first-time-9-months-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-08-01/</link><description>中国低迷的制造业即将迎来“残酷的夏天”，本周的两项信心调查显示，因需求疲软而苦苦挣扎的工厂主的悲观情绪达到了新的水平，预示着2024年下半年经济增长面临风险。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 01:52:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-factory-activity-contracts-first-time-9-months-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-08-01/</guid></item><item><title>加拿大军舰穿越台湾海峡，激怒中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/canadian-warship-passes-through-taiwan-strait-drawing-chinas-ire-2024-08-01/</link><description>一艘加拿大军舰通过台湾海峡，渥太华称这是对开放的印太地区的承诺，此举遭到中国指责，称 7 月 31 日的海军演习破坏了和平。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 01:29:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/canadian-warship-passes-through-taiwan-strait-drawing-chinas-ire-2024-08-01/</guid></item><item><title>中国外交部称中印将加快边界谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-india-speed-up-border-talks-says-chinese-foreign-ministry-2024-08-01/</link><description>中国外交部周四在一份声明中表示，中印将加快围绕有争议边界的谈判，继续维护该地区的和平与安宁。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 00:07:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-india-speed-up-border-talks-says-chinese-foreign-ministry-2024-08-01/</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰泽连斯基希望中国对俄罗斯施加更大压力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/zelenskiy-says-ukraine-does-not-want-china-mediator-2024-07-31/</link><description>乌克兰总统泽连斯基周三表示，基辅不希望中国在与俄罗斯长达29个月的冲突中充当调解人，但希望北京向莫斯科施加更大压力，以结束战争。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 22:17:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/zelenskiy-says-ukraine-does-not-want-china-mediator-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>早间出价：非凡的反弹席卷了所有市场</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-07-31/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 21:47:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>游泳——中国选手潘金莲打破自己保持的1亿米自由泳金牌世界纪录</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/swimming-chinas-pan-obliterates-100m-freestyle-world-record-gold-2024-07-31/</link><description>周三，中国选手潘占乐在巴黎奥运会上打破了自己保持的100米自由泳世界纪录，在该项目中夺得了令人震惊的金牌，并击败了众多冠军对手。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 20:53:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/swimming-chinas-pan-obliterates-100m-freestyle-world-record-gold-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>美国立法者寻求阻止中国企业获得太阳能制造补贴</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/us-lawmakers-seek-block-chinese-firms-solar-manufacturing-subsidy-2024-07-31/</link><description>美国两党议员小组周三提出了一项法案，禁止中国太阳能电池板制造商为其美国工厂申请补贴。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 19:52:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/us-lawmakers-seek-block-chinese-firms-solar-manufacturing-subsidy-2024-07-31/</guid></item></channel></rss>